    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You make the most of your armor's magical capabilities.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Dex 13, base attack bonus +11 or fighter level 8th, armor training class feature, proficiency with light armor.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You add your armor's enhancement bonus as a bonus on your initiative checks.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 5 stamina points as an immediate action to gain a circumstance bonus on your Reflex saves equal to your armor's enhancement bonus for 1 turn. (See page 17.)",
